  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A gunshot echoes through the tunnels of the New York subway system. A secret service agent lies dying, and Diaz, with a gun gripped tightly in his hand, flees and stumbles into a strange underground world where a secret society of genetically engineered hybrid clones threaten to subvert the population of the outside world. Experience New York City's secret night life in Hybrid Heaven, a unique, fully-immersive action RPG that combines fighting, action, and role playing into a story of alien invasion, scientific experimentation, and murder. Unravel the secrets of the hybrid society, the future of humanity, and the true identity of Diaz.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
